862
00:48:23,420 --> 00:48:25,670
Of course not.

863
00:48:25,670 --> 00:48:29,580
We staged this surprise reunion,
so you two can make up.

864
00:48:29,580 --> 00:48:32,520
Gosh, make up for what? That was so long ago.

865
00:48:32,520 --> 00:48:34,200
What happened to you two?

866
00:48:34,200 --> 00:48:36,470
