on an ancestral ritual table

894
00:51:55,330 --> 00:51:57,070
instead of alcohol.

895
00:51:57,070 --> 00:51:58,750
Yes, you can.

896
00:51:58,750 --> 00:52:01,590
- This is not right.
- It is right.

897
00:52:01,590 --> 00:52:04,690
Oppa, you speak up.

898
00:52:04,690 --> 00:52:07,820
- Well...
- He has nothing to say.

899
00:52:07,820 --> 00:52:09,840
His daughter broke off her engagement for booze.

900
00:52:09,840 --> 00:52:11,250
- What?
- What?

901
00:52:11,250 --> 00:52:13,600
- Broke off her engagement?
- What do you mean over booze?

902
00:52:13,600 --> 00:52:15,400
What do you mean by that?

903
00:52:15,400 --> 00:52:18,240
She called off the wedding
because he nagged her about booze.

904
00:52:18,240 --> 00:52:20,280
Incredible, right?

