907
00:52:27,520 --> 00:52:29,120
The eldest son of the family

908
00:52:29,120 --> 00:52:31,410
who taught them how to drink from a young age.

909
00:52:31,410 --> 00:52:32,790
And all of you,

910
00:52:32,790 --> 00:52:35,330
who offered endless booze
at gatherings, played a part, too.

911
00:52:35,330 --> 00:52:37,380
Am I wrong?

912
00:52:37,380 --> 00:52:39,140
If you feel any morsel of responsibility,

913
00:52:39,140 --> 00:52:41,770
don't mention alcohol again.

914
00:52:46,080 --> 00:52:47,370
I will...

915
00:52:48,180 --> 00:52:49,660
just trust and wait.

916
00:52:49,660 --> 00:52:52,150
My Geum Ju is not a thoughtless kid,

917
00:52:52,150 --> 00:52:53,930
so she'll quit drinking.

918
00:52:53,930 --> 00:52:55,990
She'll never go near alcohol again-

919
00:52:55,990 --> 00:52:58,080
I'm home!

920
00:53:05,390 --> 00:53:08,360
Why do you keep running away?

921
00:53:16,960 --> 00:53:18,810
Uncle!

922
00:53:19,910 --> 00:53:21,560
Auntie!

923
00:53:22,660 --> 00:53:24,620
You're here to see me?

924
00:53:24,620 --> 00:53:26,560
Right, today's Grandpa's memorial...

925
00:53:26,560 --> 00:53:28,240
Geum Ju.

926
00:53:28,240 --> 00:53:30,940
Why the hell did you show up drunk?

927
00:53:30,940 --> 00:53:34,080
We can't even put liquor
on the ceremony table because of you!

928
00:53:34,080 --> 00:53:35,550
What did you say?

929
00:53:36,550 --> 00:53:39,340
What? There's really no booze there.

930
00:53:39,340 --> 00:53:42,310
Gosh, Grandpa loved to drink.

931
00:53:42,310 --> 00:53:43,850
Gosh, no wonder.

932
00:53:43,850 --> 00:53:46,090
I knew why I was pulled to...

933
00:53:46,090 --> 00:53:48,660
buy this today when I saw this.

934
00:53:48,660 --> 00:53:50,000
I...

